@startuml MCP Server - Sequence Diagram
title MCP Server 端到端时序图

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam participantPadding 10
skinparam boxPadding 10

' 定义参与者
actor "LLM Client\n(Claude Desktop)" as Client
participant "Config\n(Singleton)" as Config
participant "Logger\n(Singleton)" as Logger
participant "McpServerRunner" as Runner
participant "JsonRpc" as JR
participant "McpServer" as Mcp
participant "ToolManager" as TM
participant "ResourceManager" as RM
participant "File System" as FS
participant "System APIs" as SysAPI

' 根据部署模式选择传输层
note over Client, Runner
    <b>两种部署模式:</b>
    1. STDIO: 通过 stdin/stdout (LSP格式)
    2. HTTP: 通过网络 (JSON-RPC)
end note

' =============================================
' 启动阶段
' =============================================

== 启动阶段 ==

Client -> Config: main() 开始\nConfig::getInstance()
activate Config
Config --> Client: 配置加载完成
deactivate Config

Client -> Logger: Logger::getInstance().initialize()
activate Logger
Logger --> Client: 日志系统初始化完成
deactivate Logger

Client -> Runner: new McpServerRunner(config)
activate Runner

Runner -> JR: new JsonRpc()
activate JR
JR --> Runner: JSON-RPC 处理器创建
deactivate JR

Runner -> Mcp: new McpServer(mcpConfig)
activate Mcp

Mcp -> TM: new ToolManager()
activate TM
TM --> Mcp: 工具管理器创建
deactivate TM

Mcp -> RM: new ResourceManager()
activate RM
RM --> Mcp: 资源管理器创建
deactivate RM

Mcp -> Logger: new PromptManager()\n(内部使用Logger)
activate Logger
Logger --> Mcp: 提示管理器创建
deactivate Logger

Mcp --> Runner: MCP 服务器创建完成
deactivate Mcp

Runner -> Mcp: registerMethods(*jsonRpc_)
activate Mcp
note right
    注册7个MCP方法:
    • initialize
    • tools/list, tools/call
    • resources/list, resources/read
    • prompts/list, prompts/get
end note
Mcp --> Runner: 方法注册完成
deactivate Mcp

Runner -> Runner: 创建传输层\n(HTTP/STDIO/BOTH)

Runner --> Client: 服务器启动完成\n开始监听请求
deactivate Runner

' =============================================
' 工具调用流程
' =============================================

== 工具调用 (tools/call) ==

Client -> Runner: HTTP POST / 或\nstdin (LSP格式)
note left
    <b>HTTP请求:</b>
    POST /\n{"jsonrpc":"2.0",\n "method":"tools/call",\n "params":{...},\n "id":1}

    <b>STDIO请求:</b>
    Content-Length: 123\n\n{"jsonrpc":"2.0",...}
end note

activate Runner
Runner -> JR: handleRequest(jsonString)
activate JR

JR -> JR: deserializeRequest(jsonStr)
JR -> JR: handleRequest(Request)
JR -> JR: processRequest()

JR -> Mcp: syncHandler("tools/call", params)
activate Mcp

Mcp -> TM: callTool(name, arguments)
activate TM
TM -> TM: 查找工具 (加锁)
TM -> TM: 验证参数

TM -> TM: handler(name, arguments)
note right
    <b>用户定义的工具处理函数:</b>
    例如: get_current_time 工具
    调用 std::chrono::system_clock
end note

TM -> SysAPI: 调用系统API\n(e.g., std::chrono)
activate SysAPI
SysAPI --> TM: 返回系统时间
deactivate SysAPI

TM --> Mcp: 返回 ToolResult
deactivate TM

Mcp --> JR: 返回 JSON 结果
deactivate Mcp

JR -> JR: serializeResponse(response)
JR --> Runner: 返回 JSON 响应
deactivate JR

Runner --> Client: HTTP Response 或\nstdout (LSP格式)
note left
    <b>HTTP响应:</b>
    {"jsonrpc":"2.0",\n "result":{"content":[...]},\n "id":1}

    <b>STDIO响应:</b>
    Content-Length: 456\n\n{"jsonrpc":"2.0",...}
end note
deactivate Runner

' =============================================
' 资源读取流程
' =============================================

== 资源读取 (resources/read) ==

Client -> Runner: resources/read 请求
activate Runner
Runner -> JR: handleRequest(jsonString)
activate JR
JR -> JR: deserializeRequest
JR -> JR: processRequest()

JR -> Mcp: syncHandler("resources/read", params)
activate Mcp

Mcp -> RM: readResource(uri)
activate RM
RM -> RM: 查找资源 (加锁)
RM -> RM: handler(uri)

RM -> FS: 读取文件内容
activate FS
FS --> RM: 返回文件内容
deactivate FS

RM --> Mcp: 返回 ResourceContent
deactivate RM

Mcp --> JR: 返回 JSON 结果
deactivate Mcp
JR -> JR: serializeResponse
JR --> Runner: JSON 响应
deactivate JR
Runner --> Client: 返回资源内容
deactivate Runner

' =============================================
' 错误处理
' =============================================

== 错误处理场景 ==

Client -> Runner: tools/call\n(不存在的工具)
activate Runner
Runner -> JR: handleRequest
activate JR
JR -> Mcp: syncHandler("tools/call", params)
activate Mcp
Mcp -> TM: callTool(name, args)
activate TM

TM -> TM: 查找工具 - 未找到

TM --> Mcp: 返回错误
deactivate TM
Mcp --> JR: 返回错误响应
deactivate Mcp
JR -> JR: 序列化错误
JR --> Runner: JSON-RPC Error
deactivate JR
Runner --> Client: {"jsonrpc":"2.0",\n"error":{"code":-32601,...},\n"id":1}
deactivate Runner

' =============================================
' 图例说明
' =============================================

legend right
    <b>图例说明:</b>

    |<back:back: #E8F5E9> 绿色 | 客户端 |
    |<back:back: #FFF3E0> 橙色 | 服务器组件 |
    |<back:back: #E0F2F1> 青色 | 业务管理器 |
    |<back:back: #FFE0B2> 深橙色 | 外部系统 |

    <b>数据流向:</b>
    → 同步调用
    --> 返回结果
endlegend

@enduml
